description: Aspose.Diagram is a class library for working with Microsoft Visio files. It allows developers to create new diagrams and work with VSD, VSDX, VSTX, VSSX, VSS, VST, VSX, VTX, VDW and VDX files on ASP.NET web applications, web services and Windows applications. It allows you to open files and manipulate the elements of the diagram, from lines and fills, to more complex elements, and then export to VDX, VSX,VSDX,VSSX,VSTX, VTX, XPS, HTML, SVG, SWF, XAML, image or PDF formats.
releaseNotes:
This release introduces the features, enhancements,task and bug fixes as detailed below:
   
   Enhancements 
   DIAGRAMNET-50016-Add support to duplicate / clone a shape
   DIAGRAMNET-50677-Provide the single API to convert a Visio shape to PDF
   DIAGRAMNET-50678-Provide the single API to convert a Visio shape to HTML
     
    Bugs 
   DIAGRAMNET-50762-The parsing error of the long attributes value occurred while generating a VDX diagram
   DIAGRAMNET-51401-Output VSDX - the controls in Shapes do not work
   DIAGRAMNET-51402-VSDX to image - an OLE object is not preserved 
   DIAGRAMNET-51406-VSD to image - the additional characters appear
   DIAGRAMNET-51410-VSD to PDF - the page number remains 4 in all pages
   DIAGRAMNET-51411-VSD to image - the page number remains 4 in all pages
   DIAGRAMNET-51414-VSDX to PDF - missing the content of shapes
   DIAGRAMNET-51415-VSDX to PDF - incorrect background color of the shapes
   DIAGRAMNET-51416-VSDX to HTML - incorrect background color of the shapes
